<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She ringed in her 39th birthday with a celebratory dinner on Monday night.  </p>

<p>And Ashley Roberts had a spring in her step as she headed to Global Studios to present her showbiz segment on the Heart Radio Breakfast Show on Wednesday.</p>

<p>The Pussycat Dolls singer, 39, turned heads in a silk floral and Dalmatian print maxi dress.</p>

<p>Strutting her stuff: Ashley Roberts turned heads as she arrived at Global Studios in London  to present her showbiz segment on the Heart Radio Breakfast Show on Wednesday</p>

<p>The dress featured a keyhole neckline and a thigh-high slit which teased a hint of Ashley's tanned and toned legs. </p>

<p>The former Strictly star complemented her outfit with nude heels, sunglasses and a black chainmail bag. </p>

<p>She wore her blonde locks up in a high bun and finished off her stylish ensemble with a polished make-up look.  </p>

<p>She's got style: The Pussycat Dolls singer, 39, looked super chic in a silk floral and Dalmatian print maxi dress</p>

<p>Striking display: The dress featured a keyhole neckline and a thigh-high slit which teased a hint of Ashley's tanned and toned legs</p>

<p>Gorgeous: The former Strictly star complemented her outfit with nude heels, sunglasses and a black chainmail bag</p>

<p>The singer appeared in high spirits as she arrived by taxi.  </p>

<p>On Monday night, Ashley stepped out for dinner at La Famiglia in Chelsea to mark the milestone of her 39th birthday.  </p>

<p>Earlier in the day, the singing sensation treated her Instagram followers to a racy new bikini snap to mark the occasion.  </p>

<p>Happy:The singer appeared in high spirits as she arrived by taxi</p>

<p>The blonde beauty showed off her incredible physique in a matching two-piece while posing for the playful image. </p>

<p>Referencing her birthday and Britain's unseasonably warm September weather in an accompanying caption, she wrote: 'Ring Ring: Alexa says it’s 30 degrees and my birthday hunni’s. Thank you for all your lovely messages!!!'  </p>

<p>The post prompted an inevitable wave of positive comments from fans, among them former Strictly Come Dancing champion Stacey Dooley, who wrote: 'WELL WELL WELL, happy bday sis.' </p>

<p>Earlier that day Ashley admitted she had been spoiled with cakes, champagne and cards from her extended family at Heart Radio after turning up for her role as showbiz correspondent. </p>

<p>The singer shared an Instagram video showing a caterpillar cake, a sumptuous-looking white chocolate creation, a bottle of Taittinger champagne and Hypnotiq fruit liqueur to kick off her day of celebrations.  </p>

<p>Here we go: On Monday, the singing sensation treated her Instagram followers to a racy new bikini snap to mark her 39th birthday</p>
